@host = https://localhost:7175
@hostHttp = http://localhost:5203

### Reference — health check (works out of the box)
GET {{host}}/books/health

### Exercise 1 — list all books
GET {{host}}/books

### Exercise 2 — get by id
GET {{host}}/books/1
###
GET {{host}}/books/999

### Exercise 3 — create a book
POST {{host}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Refactoring",
  "author": "Martin Fowler",
  "publishedYear": 1999
}

### Exercise 4 — update a book
PUT {{host}}/books/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Pragmatic Programmer (20th Anniversary)",
  "publishedYear": 2019
}

### Exercise 5 — delete a book
DELETE {{host}}/books/3

### Exercise 6 — search with query strings
GET {{host}}/books/search?author=Martin
###
GET {{host}}/books/search?year=1999

### Exercise 7 — controller routes (after enabling MapControllers)
GET {{host}}/api/books
###
GET {{host}}/api/books/2
